title: Cocoto Fishing Master [USA] [PS2DVD]
description: The magic whirlpool is overflowing with with lava. If it continues, all of the Abysses, as well as all the other worlds will be engulfed by lava. Only the 5 millennial fish know the secrets of the whirlpool. Cocoto must travel the world and fish in order to find them and save the world. Climb into our boat, grab your fishing rod, choose your bait, then off you go, big game fishing in the 5 fantasy lakes that are filled with surprises. Discover imaginary fish and take part in a unique gaming experience with the virtual fishing rod that is compatible with this game.
